City TEXT /*Examples: 'Aberdeen '*/,
AirportCode TEXT /*Examples: 'AAF'*/,
AirportName TEXT /*Examples: 'Phillips AAF '*/,

);

Airline INTEGER /*Examples: 1*/,
FlightNo INTEGER /*Examples: 28*/,
SourceAirport TEXT /*Examples: ' APG'*/,
DestAirport TEXT /*Examples: ' ASY'*/,
PRIMARY KEY (Airline, FlightNo),
